The '''Barrckli''' were a social group with [[Unidentified Barrckli|one member]] present on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Darkknell/Legends|Darkknell]]<ref name="IAD">{{StoryCite|story=Interlude at Darkknell|book=Tales from the New Republic}}</ref> in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].<ref name="IADdate">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]'' dates the events of "[[Interlude at Darkknell]]" to [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].</ref> While at the [[Continuum Void]] [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]], the Barrckli was in a drunken state and the professional [[Con artist/Legends|con artist]] [[Moranda Savich]] had to dodge past the individual while exiting the cantina's [[Refresher/Legends|refresher]].<ref name="IAD" />

==Behind the scenes==
A Barrckli appeared in [[Timothy Zahn]]'s Part I of the short story "[[Interlude at Darkknell]]," included in the [[1999]] ''[[Tales from the New Republic]]'' anthology.<ref name="IAD" />

